snippet.title: MLB Power Pros 2008 (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description: The opening cinematic from MLB Power Pros 2008, a baseball video game by Konami. Starring Ichiro, Johan Santana, Albert Pujols, Vladimir Guerrero, Alex Rodriguez, etc.
